data.description: LOOK! The Nelson Hill home you have been waiting for! 2 car garage, mature landscaping and nice front porch. This home is well taken care of and boasts dark wood laminate flooring in living room and halls. 12 inch floor tile in the kitchen . Kitchen island, gorgeous backslash and stainless steel appliances. Large pantry and eat in kitchen/dining area. Split floorplan with primary bedroom on one side and kids rooms on the other. Primary bathroom has tiled WALK-IN shower and separate jetted tub. Termite bonded. Gutters and downspouts! Fully fenced in yard and home is just steps from the community park and lake.
